<td width="165pt">Former vice chair and head of bond trading at <a href="/wiki/Salomon_Brothers" title="Salomon Brothers">Salomon Brothers</a>; MBA, <a href="/wiki/University_of_Chicago" title="University of Chicago">University of Chicago</a></td>
