<td>Leading scholar in finance; Ph.D., <a href="/wiki/Massachusetts_Institute_of_Technology" title="Massachusetts Institute of Technology">Massachusetts Institute of Technology</a>; Professor at <a href="/wiki/Harvard_University" title="Harvard University">Harvard University</a></td>
