<tr>
<td><a href="/wiki/Victor_Haghani" title="Victor Haghani">Victor Haghani</a></td>
<td>Arbitrage group at Salomon; Masters in Finance, <a href="/wiki/London_School_of_Economics" title="London School of Economics">LSE</a></td>
</tr>
